- Extracted R_4 = {P1, P2} with μ(P1) = 1/2, μ(P2) = 1/2

**After solving F_5:**
- Extracted R_5 = {P3, P4} with μ(P3) = 1/4, μ(P4) = 1/4

**Build MCF(5) Input:**

Commodities S_5:
